{"tid":384399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[俄佬助攻定口炮]普京指朝鮮半島接近爆大規模衝突","createTime":"2017-09-02T09:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T02:14:22.000Z","uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69d6710e0eb54032ceab42716c2a672d1428e2ee","tid":384399,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:15:59.000Z","msg":"美韓兩國元首同意加強南韓的國防力量，應對北韓的挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普與南韓總統文在寅通電話，磋商朝鮮半島局勢和應對方案，雙方一致認為有必要加強南韓的國防建設，同意修訂《韓美導彈指南》。指南在2012年簽署，將南韓的導彈射程由三百公里提高至八百公里，但攜帶的彈頭不可超過五百公斤。南韓一直都希望修訂指南，增加可攜帶彈頭的重量。<br />\n<br />\n兩人又重申對北韓採取最大程度制裁及壓力，迫使北韓重返談判桌。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京就警告，朝鮮半島局勢持續惡化，接近爆發大規模衝突；又指企圖透過施壓迫使北韓停止發展核武是錯的，呼籲以直接對話解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=234566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D234566&d=RYzsNvr9Civu4n4MXYouBpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=6d063955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D234566&h=643a91f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=234566</a>"},{"pid":"bc32d320b003a46991d27e46c02d3fd3e1ea3708","tid":384399,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e4c8fe4cdf57d82302e7fd99bed45b4606269e","tid":384399,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"沙皇準備抽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff335300d0ddb5068b0e10a519fa09efc703d97","tid":384399,"uid":134202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙皇準備抽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />